reviewText: This film will show you how to fight in minutes not years! Be a skilled martial artist in just a few days.wow!!

Like Jeet Kune Do, I'll keep this review simple and direct. This DVD is  the best I have ever seen. If you study Jeet Kune Do or just interested in self defense get this DVD. If your only interested in self defense, you will want to study JKD after seeing this DVD. I suggest you try Sifu Strongs 4 DVD set. All 4 are JKD at a higher level.

 JKDpupil71

The DVD is in Chinese.  It does not say that anywhere in the discription of the DVD.

If you speak the language have fun and let us know what you think.
